Key Match Events: Elias Mokwana scored a goal for Bafana Bafana
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played in Brazzaville, Republic of Congo
Others: Bafana Bafana will have to beat Uganda in Kampala in November to ensure consecutive qualification for the Africa Cup of Nations
If Bafana fail to get victory in Kampala they will have another chance to qualify ahead of the Congo as long as they beat South Sudan at home on November 19
